name: Bethany Hall-Long
tweet: As the chair of the Behavioral Health Consortium, I am proud that our state is one of four in which the overdose deaths percentage saw a decrease, despite our national average. I promise to continue to work to facilitate changes for a healthcare system that works for all! #DESOTS

tweet: The resilience of the Delawarean spirit during these past two years has kept our state’s economy strong and prosperous despite the pandemic, and we are beyond hopeful for the future ahead. #DESTOS
